N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4103.5 - Misinformation

State Regulations

Any person giving, or attempting to give, misleading or
inaccurate information of a horse's performance for inclusion in a printed
racing program, shall be subject to the penalties provided by this

Subchapter. Notes
